<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07948</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT TO ESTABLISH A NATIONAL CENTER FOR INFORMATION AND TECHNICAL ASSISTANCE RELATING TO ALL TYPES OF FAMILY RESOURCE AND SUPPORT PROGRAMS</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Promotes parental competencies to build a healthy development of both parents and children by stimulating the development and expansion of family resource and support program; encourage early intervention of such programs with families to improve problem situations before such situations become crises; and assist parents in enhancing their children’s development.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : "Lingkod Pamilya Act of 2018.”</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>SY-ALVARADO, JOSE ANTONIO &quot;KUYA JONATHAN&quot; R.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-07-24</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON POPULATION AND FAMILY RELATIONS ON 2018-08-01</td></tr></table>